description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the next post (after his last post made on May 22, 2024) made by CZ's verified X account (https://x.com/cz_binance) contains the numeric digit "4" or the exact word "four" anywhere within its text. This market will also resolve to "Yes" if the next post on CZ's verified X account contains a picture of CZ holding up four fingers. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If no new posts are made to this X account by October 31, 2024, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to "No".

For the purposes of this market, all quote and reply posts count toward a "Yes" resolution, but reposts will not count.

Pluralization/possessive, as well as variance in capitalizations will count toward the resolution of this market, however variant spellings will not count. Other and extraneous symbols being inserted into the word “four” (ex: "f0ur") are considered variant spellings, and will not count toward in a "Yes" resolution.

The resolution source for this market will be Changpeng Zhao's verified X account: https://x.com/cz_binance.

Please note, only the @cz_binance verified X account counts for this market, regardless of the URL for this profile. If Changpeng Zhao posts from another account, it has no bearing on the resolution of this market.
